question: Give me all stringers and editors paid 2000.
sql_query1:
SELECT Authors.Name 
FROM Authors
WHERE (Authors.Classification = "Stringer" OR Authors.Classification = "Editor") AND Authors.Payment = 2000
sql_query2:
SELECT Authors.Name 
FROM Authors
WHERE Authors.Classification = "Stringer" OR Authors.Classification = "Editor" AND Authors.Payment = 2000
interpretation1: Show all stringers paid 2000, also show the editors paid the same amount.
interpretation2: Show all the stringers listed, then show the editors, but only those paid 2000.
